Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:37.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）早河\Nそちらの作業は進んでいるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:34.75,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Hayakawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.51,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,how are things progressing on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:40.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河・通信）絶園の魔法使いが\N御柱への攻撃を→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.29,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,I've already leaked information
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:43.51,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,that the mage of Exodus plans to attack the Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,画策しているという情報は\Nすでに流した。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）\N現場にいる艦が　どう対応するか→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:46.63,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,I'm certain the fleet will decide to respond,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:49.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある程度の意志統一は\N図られているだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:49.30,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,at least in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門・通信）ある程度か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.53,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,To an extent?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:55.78,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,Ultimately, it depends on how things go,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:56.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）結局　出たとこ勝負だろうが\N死ぬなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.05,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門・通信）己の行いを顧みれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.64,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Considering my past actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このあたりで　それくらいの報いを\N受けそうだがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.37,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,I imagine things might finally catch up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:06.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ\N行いが悪いのは　お互いさまだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:06.24,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,We're in this together, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に　ぶざまに死なれると→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.27,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,If you suffer a gruesome death,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらも将来が心配になる。\Nふっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.33,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,I'll have to worry about my own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:14.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フロイラインたちは\Nすでに日本を出て→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:14.78,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,The Fräulein's group has since left Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:16.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船や供物の手配中だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.98,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,They requisitioned a ship and some offerings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:22.11,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Junichiro and I will be leaving tomorrow, along with the princess and Hanemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:20.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と潤一郎は　姫様と羽村を伴い→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日には出立する。　そして→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:26.44,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Fuwa Mahiro and Takigawa Yoshino will be coming as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不破真広と滝川吉野も共にな。\N（早河・通信）何ぃ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.64,Default,Haya,0,0,0,,What?!
