Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:40.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫ガチャ（ドアの音）\N（不破真広）おう　呼んだか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.98,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,You wanted something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）あっ　あの…。\Nあっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:41.87,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:46.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広君\Nもし　僕に何かあったら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:46.38,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Mahiro, if anything happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.42,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,can you mail this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）これを出してほしいんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振られた彼女宛てか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.42,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,To that girl who dumped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:56.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん。　無事に帰って来れたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:54.66,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:58.00,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,It won't be necessary if I come back in one piece, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必要ないんだけど…。\Nはぁ～。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ　なんてことするんだい！→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.38,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,H-How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.97,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,It took me three whole days to write that.{slow}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,書くのに３日かかったのに～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.56,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:15.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのな　お前に何かあったら\Nその時点で　世界は終わりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:15.35,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,If anything happens to you, the world is doomed anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:18.82,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,If you have something to say to her, stay alive and tell her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:18.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言いたいことがあるなら\N生きて帰って　直接　言え。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけどさ\N映画の主人公みたいに→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:21.71,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,But I might end up like a movie hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨て身の攻撃で　はじまりの樹に\N勝利するって展開もあるだろう!?→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.41,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,launching a final, desperate attack on the Tree and actually succeeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.96,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,You know, both sides taking each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　相打ちってやつだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\N映画の主人公じゃねぇだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.37,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,You're not a movie hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨て身の攻撃で負けたらどうする。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.33,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,What if that last-ditch effort doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだら意味がねぇんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.88,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Dying is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）真広君…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.28,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Mahiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((はぁ　はぁ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）\N((どうしたの？　二人して改まって))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.73,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.64,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,Both of you look so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（滝川吉野）\N((僕たちも　御柱破壊チームに→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:56.23,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,We'd like to join the Pillar assault team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入れてほしいんです))\N（羽村）((ええ～!?→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.35,Defalics,Hane,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.11,Defalics,Hane,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわ～　痛っ　痛っ！　痛ててっ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）((御柱近くでは\N鎖部の魔法は使えないうえに→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.26,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,You already know Kusaribe magic won't work near the Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:07.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秘密裏に\N御柱近海へ近づかねばならない。→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:07.07,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,Plus, this has to be a covert operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行動しやすい少人数が望まれるの))\N((はっきり言えよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.23,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,The smaller the group, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.33,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Just cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あなたたちは　足手まといよ))\N((言ってくれるな))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.08,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,You'd hold us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.86,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((僕たちのことは\N放置してもらってかまいません))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.02,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,You don't need to keep us safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((命の危険にあっても→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.70,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Even if we get into danger, don't try to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けは不要です))\N（葉風）((そんな…))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.67,Defalics,Hakaze,0,0,0,,But that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.59,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,Taking you near the Pillar is too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）((さすがに\N御柱付近に連れていくのは危険よ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）((ほかの鎖部の者たちは→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:31.67,Defalics,Hakaze,0,0,0,,The other Kusaribe members are guarding the Tree of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹を\N見張ることになっている。→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二人は　そちらに…))\N((すみません))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.15,Defalics,Hakaze,0,0,0,,You two should help with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.47,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:38.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((でも　僕は\N何かが起ころうとしている→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:38.42,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,but I know something big is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その中心に行きたいんです))\N（葉風）((吉野！))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.06,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,and I want to be there when it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.06,Defalics,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.61,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,You guys are using my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.37,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,It only makes sense that I take the lead on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:47.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((だったら\N責任者を連れていくのは当然だ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.42,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((違うか？))\N（山本）((真広君の作戦は→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:53.87,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,It's not as though your plan was particularly great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:53.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰しも考えられる選択肢の\N一つよ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:56.21,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,We only settled on it because we had nothing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局　それしかないから\N受け入れただけ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.88,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,And the one who decided we had nothing better was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((それしかないを決定したのは\N俺だろ？))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:03.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((はぁ～　まったく　あんたは…。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.88,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're such a...{nigger}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に放っておくわよ。\N泣いても知らないからね))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.24,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,We really {\i0}will{\i1} leave you guys behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.18,Defalics,Yama,0,0,0,,You'd better not regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.34,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ありがとうございます))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:14.90,Defalics,Hane,0,0,0,,You say that dying is meaningless,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:15.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（心の声）≪死んだら意味がない\N君は　そう言うけど…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:19.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら　ますます　君が行く意味は\Nなくなってしまうのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:19.69,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,but that would mean your coming along is even more meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.46,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？\N（羽村）あっ　いや…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.77,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）サンキュー\Nフォー　ウエイティング！→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:27.15,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レンタル料\Nギリギリまで値切れたわ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.36,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,I managed to talk down our ship's rental fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:34.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,浮いたお金で　今夜は豪遊ね！\N（哲馬）考えるだに無謀だな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.87,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,We're going all out with this extra money tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.79,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,This plan is foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:38.78,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,Taking on a hundred cruisers with just one ship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった１隻で\N１００隻の武装艦を相手に→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.72,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,and with only seven of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:42.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも　僅か７名で…。\N（山本）問題ないわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:41.92,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,That's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:45.30,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Magic can increase our speed and defense
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,速度と防御は\N魔法で強化できるし→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,航行の際も　完全に船体を隠せる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.01,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,as well as conceal our ship's approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:53.45,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,However, Kusaribe magic will not be effective in the vicinity of the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）しかし\N艦艇が現在いる海域では→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎖部の魔法を使えません。\N事実上→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:57.10,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,The fact remains that only Hanemura will be able to approach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羽村以外は　艦艇に近づけない。\N（山本）ふふふっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:02.43,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,That's exactly the point Fuwa Mahiro's plan addresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためにあるのが\N不破真広の作戦でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:06.22,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,If we can force the fleet into an area where Kusaribe magic is viable,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,艦艇を　魔法が使える海域に→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引きずり出せれば\N勝機はあるじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.74,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,we'll have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.26,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,You would place that much faith in the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）小僧の戯れ言を\Nそこまで信じるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）責任者として\Nここまで来ると言ってるし→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.48,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Well, he even insisted on taking the lead himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:20.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イレギュラーがあったら\Nそのつど　修正させるわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.30,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,If anything unexpected comes up, I'll have him make adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）彼らが来ることを\Nあんなに反対していたのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.84,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,At first, you most certainly did not want them to come along,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,随分と肩入れしているようですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.22,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,yet now, you support their decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.51,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,I guess I do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）わっ！　やだ　ほんとだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:32.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふっ　特別な時に→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:35.43,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,"In a special place at a special time," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:35.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特別な場所にいる少年たち…　か。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:40.01,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Well, no point in worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）まっ\N心配しても　しかたないって。→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.64,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,We should start getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く準備を進めましょう！\N（哲馬）うわっ！　なっ　何をする!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.73,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:47.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと　問題は　その格好よね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:47.38,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,We can't have you going dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:55.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）\Nう～ん…　ちょっと多すぎかなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.95,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,This might be going overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）これは置いてこうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.12,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I guess I could leave it behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっ　これ→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.90,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Is this full of magazines?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部　写真集ですか？\Nうん。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.93,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:09.18,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Visualizing and then animating static images is good for improving focus.{i wonder how this improves your focus}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静止画像で\N揺れるさまを想像すると→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい精神統一になるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも　データじゃダメなんだよね。\N絶対に紙。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.54,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,They can't be virtual images either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:12.63,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,It's got to be on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.89,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…　そうですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野君は　随分　荷物が少ないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.47,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,You aren't bringing much luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.54,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい。　準備とか心構えとか→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.90,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Mahiro showed me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どれだけ綿密にしても\N意味がないって→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:25.35,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,how useless it would be to try to prepare myself in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広に教わりましたから。　うわっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:26.19,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Whoa!{entering pissed off Hakaze}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）葉風ちゃん。\N葉風さん。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.58,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Hakaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.23,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Miss Hakaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）心構えのない者が→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.57,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,I can't believe that someone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:36.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決戦の地に出向こうとはな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.28,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,would head into a decisive battle utterly unprepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ～あ　ただの女の子だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.53,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.24,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I guess she's just a girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:44.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ\N本当に　そうなるんですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.38,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Soon enough, I suppose she really will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）\Nああ　作戦がうまくいけばね。→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:45.54,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.18,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,if everything goes as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:52.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹を倒せば\N葉風ちゃんだけではなく→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.42,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,If the Tree is defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.92,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,not only Hakaze
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.70,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,but the entire clan will be unable to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎖部一族は　魔法を使えなくなる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）確か　この辺りで\N待っているはずなのだが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.76,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,She should be around here, waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）はぁ　はぁ…。\N≪（山本）団体さ～ん→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:08.02,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Everyone! Over here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっち　こっち～！→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお～！\N溶け込んでるなぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.86,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,She fits right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.75,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,How humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）屈辱！\N耐えてください。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.96,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,Please bear with it.{suffering!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:22.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大舞台を前に　鎖部の鉄の意志が\N試されているのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:22.83,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,Our clan's iron resolve is being tested before the grand finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.83,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Let's run through the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　作戦を　ざっと洗い直すか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だいたい\N御柱から３０キロ離れた地点→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.00,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Approximately 300 km from the Pillar,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:34.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この艦艇の輪がある所から\N１０キロ以上離れた付近に→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:34.57,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,or a little over 10 km from the ring of cruisers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.09,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,we will make our stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらは陣取る。　そこで　まずは→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:41.26,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Then we'll focus on striking the survey ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この　いちばん内側にいる調査船に\N手を打つ必要がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:48.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羽村が海中を高速移動して\Nメンバーの何人かを→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:50.01,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hanemura will transport several of us underwater to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調査船へ運ぶ。\Nはい！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:50.61,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:54.57,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,It should be Junichiro, Yamamoto, and Natsumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潤一郎と　山本　夏村\Nという手はずだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:59.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）よろしくね～。\Nいや　夏村は　左門と動いてもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.10,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Take good care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.86,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,No, Natsumura should support Samon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代わりに\N俺と吉野だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.74,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Yoshino and I will go instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.31,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）ちょっと　あなたたち！\N調査船は武装してねぇし→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.39,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The survey ships are unarmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.60,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,and their crews are noncombatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:09.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗員も非戦闘員だろ？\Nしかも　魔法は使えねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.75,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Plus, Kusaribe magic will be unusable,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:13.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら　腕っぷしだけの問題だ。\N（山本）でも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.02,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,so it'll come down to physical combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.26,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.41,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The task I've given Samon is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門に任せたミッションは\N骨が折れる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.64,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,I figured he could use some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:21.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一人　必要だと考えてた。\N夏村には　そっちに回ってもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:21.11,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,That'll be you, Natsumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:21.96,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.13,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:36.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まりだ。\N潤一郎　吉野　ちょっと来てくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.15,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:35.78,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Junichiro and Yoshino, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羽村　お前もだよ。\N（羽村）あっ　ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.65,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hanemura, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.11,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.30,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回のキモは　お前なんだからな。\Nしっかりしろよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.32,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.20,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）分かってる。\Nパキッ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫（山本）あら　どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.29,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Oh, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日は早いんだから\Nもう休まないと。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.39,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,We have an early start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:56.00,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,You should be resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…\N葉風さん　見ませんでしたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.05,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Um, have you seen Miss Hakaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:02.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）寝つけず　ひと泳ぎしてくる\Nと言っておられたが。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:02.43,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,She said she was having trouble sleeping and went for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　ありがとうございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.39,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに些末な感情が\N大局を動かすこともある。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.79,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Even the most trivial emotions can affect the overall outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを見越して\N滝川吉野の参加を認めたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:16.19,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Knowing that, you allowed him to accompany us nevertheless?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:19.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふっ　どうかしらね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.78,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Well, we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　まあ　こういうのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:23.78,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Still, no man or woman is immune to the effects of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男も女も変わらないのよ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.29,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,Knowing that your loved one is watching means you'll try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:27.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きな子が見てたら\N俄然　張り切っちゃうのは。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫はぁ　はぁ　はぁ。\Nあっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さん→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.55,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Miss Hakaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:41.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます\N僕たちの参加を許してくれて。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.00,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.29,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,for allowing us to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\N許したつもりは　一度としてない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.55,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,I do not recall ever {\i1}allowing{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さん…。\N（葉風）お前は→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.36,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Miss Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:48.57,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,You know how I feel about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:50.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の気持ちを知っているな。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　お前にほれている！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:51.94,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さ…。\Nほれた男を→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.22,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Miss Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:03.45,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with wanting to keep the man I love out of harm's way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いらぬ危険に巻き込みたくないと\Nそう願うことの　どこが悪い!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に　まっすぐですね。\Nバカにしているのか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:12.67,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,You're so straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.50,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は　愛花ちゃんの死は→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:21.19,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I think I've come to terms with Aika's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け入れたつもりです。\N（葉風）吉野？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.09,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.56,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:26.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど　愛花ちゃんの死の\N必要性については…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.18,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1300)}as far as her reasoning for it goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:31.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕とは\Nまったく関係のないところでの→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.28,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I wasn't even considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花ちゃんの決断。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:37.13,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Aika decided she didn't need my help
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:37.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の助けなど\Nまったく必要ないと→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.11,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,and took care of everything on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてを自分で片づけた。\Nそれは違う！→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.53,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,That isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:43.11,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything you two could have done—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前たちには\Nどうすることもできなかっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.15,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:46.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっています！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの娘は\Nお前たちを思ってこそ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.44,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,She did it because she cared about both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:55.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは分かっています。\Nだからこそ…→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.94,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.75,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,That's why
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さんだけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.30,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,it's not just you, Miss Hakaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,山本さん　羽村さん　潤一郎さん→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:01.64,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,but also Miss Yamamoto, Hanemura, Junichiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初は敵だった左門さんたちも→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.13,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,and even former enemies like Mr. Samon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:09.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不思議な縁で出会って\N共同生活をして→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:09.44,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,A twist of fate brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:12.63,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Living together strengthened that bond,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつしか　とても関わりの強い→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大切な存在になっていった。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.80,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,and you've all become important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう僕は　大切な人たちが→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.16,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I just
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.74,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,want to be there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大切なことを決めるその瞬間に→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when those I care about make important decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関係のないところに\Nいたくないんです！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）吉野…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.86,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大切な人の戦いを見届けたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.53,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,If those I care about are fighting, I want to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さん…　うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:38.21,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Miss Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:51.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）私は助けんぞ\Nお前に何があったとしても。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.44,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,I'm not going to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.76,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,no matter what happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい。　助けてもらって→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.11,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:57.77,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,If you helped me, and it held you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:58.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足を\N引っ張るようなことになれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.78,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I couldn't look you in the eye anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　こうして　葉風さんと\N向き合うことができませんから。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）分かった。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.24,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ていろ。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.79,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.10,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Take a good look at our fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちの戦いを…　私を見ていろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.66,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:23.35,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:34.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほらよ　甘いもん追加。\N（羽村）ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.24,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Here, I ordered dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.85,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:40.15,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The plan depends on how much energy you can conserve today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日の作戦は　お前の体力を→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:40.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どれだけ温存できるかに\Nかかってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気合い入れて食えよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.36,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,so eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴクッ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）\Nほかの人が絶園の魔法使いなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.79,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,I'm sure if someone else were the mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと簡単に　はじまりの樹を\N倒せるんだろうけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:50.95,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,we'd have a much easier time with the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:54.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな。　多少の犠牲が出ても→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.52,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.33,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The plan would have a better chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと確実な策をとっただろうな。\Nうっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.79,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,even if there were a greater loss of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\N人が死にまくるような戦いを→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:58.98,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,It's not like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.63,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,you would ever back a plan that involved too many casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許せるようなヤツじゃないからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）迷惑…　かけてるよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.91,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,I'm causing trouble, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも悪くねぇって\N思ってるからこそ→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:11.03,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Not really. Everyone agrees with you, \Nand that's why they accepted this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなが乗ったんだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:16.94,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The battle at Mt. Fuji cost so many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さんざん犠牲者の出た\Nあの富士の戦い。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門も早河も　多くの人間を\N助けたいと願っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:21.23,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Samon and Hayakawa both talked about saving humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きれい事だけで言えば→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:26.24,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,If they had the power to do so, maybe there would've been fewer losses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人の犠牲者だって\N出したくなかったはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもな　お前には→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:33.14,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,but unlike them, you {\i1}do {\i0}have the power to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きれい事を\N現実にする力があるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.84,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Mahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マヒド君！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　俺が　ここに来ることには\N意味がないと言ったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:39.72,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Didn't you say my coming along would be meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）\Nうっ…　やっぱ　聞こえてたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.29,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}did{\i0} hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.08,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,But there {\i1}is{\i0} meaning in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味ならあるんだよ。　俺は→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:47.87,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,I need to see this thing through for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この目で見ておくべきなんだ。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:48.89,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の俺は\Nなんの資格も力もねぇガキだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:52.60,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm just a brat without any qualifications or abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けどな　３０年以内に→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:58.73,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,but in thirty years, I swear I'll be \Nin a position to change the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず世界を変えられる立場に\N立ってやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界を　魔法なんかなくとも→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:04.19,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,and I'm going to make it a decent place, with no need for magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっとうな形にしてみせてやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:08.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界を変えられる立場って\Nどんな立場？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:08.15,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,What kind of a position would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.61,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあな。　まあ　なんかあるだろ。\Nそんな　いいかげんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.96,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,There's gotta be {\i1}something{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.57,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,That's so wishy-washy—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:16.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！\N俺はな　お前が正直→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:17.40,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm jealous of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羨ましいんだよ。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:21.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今　その資格を持ってるのは\Nお前だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:21.45,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,You're the one who can change the world now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.57,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,so don't worry about what comes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:23.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとのことは考えるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失敗しようが\Nどれだけ犠牲を出そうが→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:27.03,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Even if you fail or it costs many lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　お前の味方だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.83,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,I'll be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:32.72,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,I'll make sure I take care of all your mistakes sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の失敗は\N俺が帳消しにしてやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな大舞台\N一生に　二度もねぇぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:36.40,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,This is the stage of a lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜい楽しんでこい。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.97,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,so enjoy the limelight!{and wipe your face, dumbass}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.17,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（研究者）現在\N御柱の周囲に配備された艦艇は→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:44.98,Default,Drone,0,0,0,,{\an8}Over a hundred cruisers are deployed around the Pillar,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１００隻を超え\N絶園の魔法使いの攻撃に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:49.54,Default,Drone,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)\an8}prepared to respond to any attack by the mage of Exodus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そろそろか。　この難局に→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.09,Defalics,Haya,0,0,0,,It's nearly time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:52.72,Defalics,Haya,0,0,0,,Will Fuwa Mahiro's plan ultimately prove itself unrealistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:52.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不破真広の作戦が\N机上の空論で終わるか→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.99,Defalics,Haya,0,0,0,,or will it be the first step in the fight to save the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界を救う最初の一手になるか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）あの少年の\N持って生まれたものが問われるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.49,Defalics,Haya,0,0,0,,We can only hope he's up to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:11.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）そろそろ\N羽村が５人を運び終えたころか。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:10.92,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,By now, it is likely that Hanemura has transported those five.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:14.66,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,If everything is going as planned, they're probably preparing for the next phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）予定では　すでに\N次の準備に入っているはずです。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.47,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）うむ。\N≫コツコツ　コツコツ（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:23.02,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,It's about time for me to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が出る時間となったようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:27.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お似合いですよ。\N（葉風）うれしくない褒め言葉だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.90,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,That suits you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.51,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,What an unpleasant compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:34.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎖部の魔法が使えるのは\Nせいぜい　ここから５キロ先まで。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:34.20,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,At best, Kusaribe magic will only work within the next five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.53,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,The Pillar will neutralize our magic if we move any closer to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上　御柱に近づけば\N無効化されます。→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,位置取りには\Nくれぐれも　ご注意を。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.57,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Be mindful of your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.59,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）艦艇１００隻\N見事　翻弄してみせよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:50.05,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Watch me throw the entire fleet into turmoil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]　ウウーー（サイレン）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:58.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ｽﾋﾟｰｶ]（船員）\Nコンタクト！　方位３３０！→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.97,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Contact at bearing 330°!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.56,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Confirmed visual on the mage of Exodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使い　確認！\N（艦長）何ぃ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.67,Default,Capt,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:01.86,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Distance: 4000.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（船員）距離４０００！\Nまっすぐ突っ込んできます！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:02.98,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,He's heading straight for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.09,Default,Capt,0,0,0,,Launch countermeasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迎撃開始！\N待ってください！→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:14.86,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Captain, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:18.74,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,If that much seawater explodes near our ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:18.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの質量の海水が\N艦の近くで破裂したら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…　どうすれば…。\N（船員）艦長！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.01,Default,Capt,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:21.63,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バシャッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（船員たち）おおっ…。\N（船員）舞姫…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:36.93,Default,Capt,0,0,0,,The Dancing Princess saved us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,舞姫に助けられた？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((葉風の扮した絶園の魔法使いが→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:44.19,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hakaze, disguised as the mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎖部の魔法が使える地点から→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.22,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,will attack the fleet with Kusaribe magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:47.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目に見える形で\N艦隊を攻撃してみせる))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:50.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そして　羽村　お前は反対に→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:48.69,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Then, Hanemura,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:54.01,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,you will appear as the Dancing Princess and deflect her onslaught.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:54.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,舞姫として出て\N葉風の攻撃をはね返す))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:57.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((実際は　かなり手前で\N葉風の魔法は無力化されるから→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.55,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hakaze's magic will be neutralized at a fair distance from the fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.99,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,so you actually only need to pretend to deflect her attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あくまで　はね返したふりだがな))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((だが　これで　舞姫が艦と御柱を→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:01.97,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,But it will fool them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:05.96,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,into believing that the Dancing Princess wishes to protect them and the Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守る気があるって印象づけられる))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:10.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）援護を！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.07,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Cover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（船員）舞姫が援護を求めている。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.88,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,The Dancing Princess wants us to cover her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ…　全艦　攻撃！→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.30,Default,Capt,0,0,0,,All ships, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.80,Default,Capt,0,0,0,,Target the mage of Exodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目標は　絶園の魔法使い！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボゥン！\Nバシュー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:28.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:32.48,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hanemura will request cover fire from the fleet \Nand proceed to attack Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((羽村は　艦の連中に援護を命じ\N葉風への攻撃に向かえ))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:35.03,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The fleet will have no problem launching a full assault on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((舞姫が守ってくれるとなれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,艦の連中は\N遠慮なく葉風へ攻撃をかける))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:38.31,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,if they think they have the Dancing Princess on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((葉風は\N御柱の周りにいる艦すべてが→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:44.64,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hakaze, go around the ring of ships as you attack them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:44.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前への攻撃に\N参加しやすいよう→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.46,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,so that the entire fleet engages you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,艦が展開している輪に\N沿うように飛べ))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカン！\N（葉風）ぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((標的は小さいし\N高速で動いている))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:03.31,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hakaze will be a small target moving at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((必ず\N前に出たくなってくるはずだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.85,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The fleet will be drawn forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((引きずり出し→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:10.90,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Once they're lured out to the area where Kusaribe magic is effective,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:12.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎖部の魔法が効く範囲に\N入ってくれれば　こっちのものだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:11.94,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,we'll have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）艦が引かれはじめたか。\N（夏村）左門殿　我々も。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.19,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,The fleet is breaking formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.28,Default,Natsu,0,0,0,,Mr. Samon, we should be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:17.94,Default,Samon,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:23.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((羽村　お前は　艦からの\Nミサイル攻撃の邪魔にならないよう→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:23.59,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hanemura, stay away from the fleet's missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風から距離を取って\N攻撃を続けろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.44,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,and continue to attack Hakaze at range.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((あくまで\N葉風が艦のいる方に飛ぶのを→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:30.58,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Make it seem like you're preventing her from closing in on the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妨害しているようにな))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:33.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカン！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.61,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Hakaze, act like the Dancing Princess is pushing you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((葉風も\N舞姫に押されている格好で→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛ぶ位置を\N少しずつ御柱から遠くし→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.18,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,and gradually retreat from the Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:48.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しでも　艦を前に出させるんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.28,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,You need to draw them out as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そして　重要なのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.16,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Bear in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:56.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風は　絶園の魔法使いらしい→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.95,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,that Hakaze must use magic like the mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.44,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,and Hanemura, like the Dancing Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:59.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羽村は　舞姫らしい\N魔法の使い方をすることだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）集中砲火は　うるさいが→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.41,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,This barrage is tiresome,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:05.74,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,but at least I have an endless supply of offerings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,供物の補充には困らんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカ　ドカ　ドカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）≪まったく\N真広は　むちゃをさせる≫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.62,Defalics,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Mahiro sure knows how to work people to their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.63,Defalics,Hakaze,0,0,0,,When will the survey ships fall back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪調査船の退避は　まだか…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（乗員）\N何が起こっている！　連絡は!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.63,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.97,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Any contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通信障害が発生してます！\N≪ガタン！（ドアの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much interference!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だっ　誰だ　お前は!?\N動くな！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.37,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:23.30,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,船底に爆発物を取り付けた。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:26.06,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,We've rigged your ships with explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:29.43,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,If I push this button, every one of them will sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを押せば\N確実に　この船は沈む！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.56,Default,Yama,0,0,0,,We only have one demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）こっちの要求は　一つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:35.30,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Take the ships as far away from the Pillar as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:35.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）大至急　御柱から\Nできるだけ離れてください。→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:38.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上は求めてないよ。\N簡単でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.25,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.53,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Simple, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.36,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,It's not safe here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:41.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに　ここも安全じゃないし。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガン！\Nザバーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）行け！\N（葉風）行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:01.11,Default,Tetsu,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.34,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.18,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Hanemura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼みます　羽村さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.31,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Now, keep going until you're clear of the Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:12.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのまま　まっすぐ\N御柱から離脱するんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪任せたぞ　羽村！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.29,Defalics,Mahiro,0,0,0,,It's all on you, Hanemura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）うっ…。\N（葉風）哲馬！→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.32,Default,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Tetsuma, if you can't keep up, they'll see through us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,精彩を欠けば気付かれるぞ！\N（哲馬）くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\N≪見えているか？　私の戦いが≫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:30.87,Defalics,Hakaze,0,0,0,,Are you watching me as I fight, Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪吉野≫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:37.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調査船の退避は　じきに終了だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.54,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,The evac operation is just about complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とうとうだね。\Nああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.17,Default,Yoshino,0,0,0,,It's come down to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.53,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつと御柱の一騎打ちだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.07,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,It'll be between the Pillar and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪葉風さん…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:44.82,Defalics,Yoshino,0,0,0,,Miss Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バキュン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.22,Default,Mahiro,0,0,0,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:11.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが御柱。→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:10.28,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,So this is the Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:13.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひるむな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:12.79,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,Don't flinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:17.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここから先は　誰の助けもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:17.13,Default,Hane,0,0,0,,No one can help you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:22.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）僕だけの戦いなんだ。
